that a little bit earlier.

00:01:58.790 --> 00:02:05.200
Her words have made us
feel, cry, and laugh.

00:02:05.200 --> 00:02:12.540
There's a real charm and poetic
theme throughout her books.

00:02:12.540 --> 00:02:17.860 position:56%
